The grid references include Grids 3-10 and C-G, which help define the structural framework. Key components visible in this section include the warehouse, office rooms, and utility rooms. The dimension '1' 3 11/16"' specifies a particular measurement within the plan. The drawing is part of sheet 370 AR 01 01, titled 'MAIN FLOOR' for the Saputo Georgetown Plant.
